node.text: I can’t believe it’s been a year since my life was changed in the most amazing way possible. Watching Tucker grow this past year has been such a bitter sweet journey. It’s crazy to look back and see how much he’s grown in just one year. Even when you’re grown you’ll always be my little buddy, Tuck man. Happy 1st birthday 💜
